import folium
import requests
import pandas

arrest_table = pandas.read_csv("https://cmsc320.github.io/files/BPD_Arrests.csv")

arrest_table = arrest_table[pandas.notnull(arrest_table["Location 1"])]

arrest_table[["lat", "long"]] = arrest_table["Location 1"].str.split(",", expand=True)
arrest_table["lat"] = arrest_table["lat"].str.replace("(", "", regex=True).astype(float)
arrest_table["long"] = arrest_table["long"].str.replace(")", "", regex=True).astype(float)

# Part 3
new_table=arrest_table.sample(500, replace=True)
for i in new_table.iterrows():
    if i[1]['sex'] == "M":
        color = 'black'
    else:
        color = 'red'
    
    html=f"""
        <ul>
            <li>Age: {i[1]['age']}</li>
            <li>Race: {i[1]['race']}</li>
            <li>Arrest Date: {i[1]['arrestDate']}</li>
            <li>Arrest Time: {i[1]['arrestTime']}</li>
            <li>Insident Offence: {i[1]['incidentOffense']}</li>
            <li>Neighborhood: {i[1]['neighborhood']}</li>
        </ul>
        """
    iframe = folium.IFrame(html=html, width=200, height=200)
    popup = folium.Popup(iframe, max_width=2650)
    
    folium.Marker(location=[i[1]['lat'], i[1]['long']], popup=popup, icon=folium.Icon(color=color)).add_to(map_osm)
    
map_osm
